With the SL Club bonus card, you can earn points that can be exchanged for nice gifts!  For you, a member of our bonus program, each subsequent visit will bring bonuses in the amount of 10% of the bill.  When paying for each order in SL Club, show the app to the waiter and earn points!

You can receive your first bonus points immediately after installing the application!
